#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks home page"
msgstr "Hjemmeside for bokmerker"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "This module lets you configure the bookmarks home page."
msgstr "Med denne modulen kan du sette opp hjemmesida for bokmerker."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view the bookmarks home page enter <userinput>bookmarks:/</userinput> in "
"the location bar."
msgstr ""
"Se hjemmesida for bokmerker ved å skrive <userinput>bookmarks:/</userinput> "
"på stedslinja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings in this module are also accessible by entering "
"<userinput>bookmarks:/config</userinput> in the location bar."
msgstr ""
"Du kan også sette opp innstillingene i denne dialogen ved å skrive "
"<userinput>bookmarks:/config</userinput> på stedslinja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "General settings"
msgstr "Generelle innstillinger"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of columns to show"
msgstr "Antall kolonner som skal vises"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Folders are automatically distributed in several columns. The optimal number "
"of columns depends on the width of the &konqueror; window and the number of "
"bookmarks you have."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show folder backgrounds"
msgstr "Vis mappebakgrunner"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable it on slow system to disable background images."
msgstr "Slå det av på langsomme systemer for å slå av bakgrunnsbilder."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show bookmarks without folder"
msgstr "Vis bokmerker uten mappe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is unchecked, bookmarks at the root of the hierarchy (not "
#| "in a folder) are not displayed. If checked, they are gathered in a \"root"
#| "\" folder."
msgid ""
"If this option is unchecked, bookmarks at the root of the hierarchy (not in "
"a folder) are not displayed. If checked, they are gathered in a “root” "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"Hvis det ikke er krysset av her, vil bokmerker i rota av hierarkiet (ikke i "
"en mappe) ikke bli vist. Hvis det er krysset av blir de samlet i en «rot»-"
"mappe."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flatten bookmarks tree"
msgstr "Flat ut bokmerketreet"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sub-folders are shown within their parent by default. If you activate this "
"option, sub-folders are displayed on their own. It looks less nice but it "
"may help if you have a very big folder you want to spread in two columns."
msgstr ""
"Undermapper vises som standard inni den overliggende mappa. Hvis dette er "
"slått på, så vises undermapper for seg selv. Det ser mindre bra ut, men kan "
"hjelpe hvis du har en svært stor mappe som du vil spre over to kolonner."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show system places"
msgstr "Vis systemsteder"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show a box with common places (Home, Network, …). Useful if you use "
"&konqueror; as a file manager."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pixmap cache"
msgstr "Pixmap-mellomlager"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disk cache size"
msgstr "Størrelsen på diskmellomlageret"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify how much disk space is used to cache the pixmaps."
msgstr "Hvor mye diskplass brukes til å mellomlagre pixmap-bildene."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear Cache"
msgstr "Tøm mellomlageret"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Remove all cached images. This may be necessary if some favicons become "
#| "corrupt and don't refresh automatically."
msgid ""
"Remove all cached images. This may be necessary if some favicons become "
"corrupt and don’t refresh automatically."
msgstr ""
"Fjern alle mellomlagrede bilder. Dette kan være nødvendig hvis noen "
"favorittikoner blir ødelagt og ikke friskes opp automatisk."
